		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />SMB2's sound engine is interesting in that you can use either the noise channel OR samples for a song's percussion, but not both at once. I'm guessing OKEATS just locks the engine into "sample mode" (amongst other things...check out the first cave in 1-1).

		

